sentences: Joshua Iniyezo (born November 8, 1988), better known by his stage name SolidStar Isoko or simply SolidStar, is a Nigerian singer, songwriter and performer.
In 2010, he released his debut album One in a Million which went on to become a huge hit.
In 2010, SolidStar formally signs to Achievas Record and his debut album was subsequently released under the label.
